text.tspan: - Methods must appear from top to bottom in the order
- Objects must appear from top to bottom in the order
- Objects and methods must have flow lines connecting
- Methods must have an origin line connecting the the
- Event triggers connect with a straight line ot the next
- Do not allow line to cross each other whenever possible.
- Flow lines should have a smooth curve if the next
element is not directly to the side of the current
- Method origin lines must always turn at 90 degree
- Lines should never require backtracking horizontal
distance to reach the originating element.
- End Points signal that the function either leads to the
next program section or loops the current section.
